Module kivakit.resource
Package com.telenav.kivakit.resource

Interface WritableResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Broadcaster, ByteSized, Listener, ModificationTimestamped, NamedObject, Readable, ReadableResource, Receiver<Transmittable>, Repeater, Resource, Resourceful, ResourcePathed, Transceiver, Transmitter<Transmittable>, Writable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    FileService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseWritableResource, File, NullResource, OutputResource, ZipEntry
    public interface WritableResource
extends Resource, Writable
    Adds the ability to write to Resource and Writable. A ResourceWriter, which provides a collection of useful methods for writing to resource, can be accessed with writer() or writer(Charset). For convenience, a PrintWriter can be retrieved with printWriter()
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
